Copyright 2026 Xocialize

Swift/MLX port of Lance (ByteDance Intelligent Creation Lab's unified multimodal model,
arXiv:2605.18678), ported from our Python MLX port (xocialize/lance-mlx, Apache-2.0).

Portions of Sources/Qwen25VL/Adapted/ are adapted from mlx-swift-lm
(https://github.com/ml-explore/mlx-swift-lm, MIT License) — specifically the Qwen2.5-VL
vision tower and language-block reference implementations, which are fileprivate upstream.

Lance model weights: Apache-2.0 (ByteDance Intelligent Creation Lab), published at
mlx-community/Lance-3B-bf16 and siblings. Wan2.2 VAE: Apache-2.0 (Alibaba).
Qwen2.5-VL: Apache-2.0 (Alibaba). This repository contains no model weights.
